column4: Tesla's Model 3 deliveries point to slower ramp up: KeyBanc
column5: Tesla Inc  is likely to deliver about 5 000 Model 3s in the fourth quarter  KeyBanc Capital Markets analysts said on Wednesday  far below the brokerage's estimate of 15 000.
